{"tid":2193950,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"林夕、柳俊江斥警方膝壓12歲女孩","createTime":"2020-09-08T08:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T08:18:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e11e5ba2a93e43fc7f48a1f9b0162e819fc79702","tid":2193950,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:18:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200908/4JMNQZLWPZAHJNXAIE3PQEV4NQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200908%2F4JMNQZLWPZAHJNXAIE3PQEV4NQ%2F&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=486993a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200908%2F4JMNQZLWPZAHJNXAIE3PQEV4NQ%2F&h=22a16de9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200908/4JMNQZLWPZAHJNXAIE3PQEV4NQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n林夕、柳俊江斥警方膝壓12歲女孩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VfcDwF1k36kcmN3D1DAK-9yrnjc=/960x720/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OKQ2PL7BGRESDFEBDGTHIMFV5Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVfcDwF1k36kcmN3D1DAK-9yrnjc%3D%2F960x720%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOKQ2PL7BGRESDFEBDGTHIMFV5Q.jpg&h=36e196c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■林夕昨fb暗寸警方無所不能，又指膝蓋很好用。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n警方前日在旺角截查年輕人時粗暴將一名年僅12歲的女孩推落地，更以膝壓方式制服，警方聲稱因女孩「拔足逃跑形迹可疑」而截查，最後女孩被票控違反限聚令，女孩母親稱事發時兄妹只是逛街及買顏料，不少市民力斥警方過份。著名填詞人林夕昨在fb連發貼文暗寸警方：「有人在自製口罩上寫明，勁揪。裝備夠勁，面對未成年少女最揪得。無所不能，無所忌憚，無事生非。究竟是誰『引發對政府的憎惡和藐視，及民間不滿』」、「膝蓋很好用，限聚令更好用，只有腦袋不好用。不如，不定期不時不高興就全城戒嚴防疫好過。」<br />\n<br />\n資深傳媒人柳俊江昨亦在fb鬧爆警方：「打完大肚婆打細路女，渣滓都不足以形容香港警察惡行。喺我想寫幾句之時，竟然有一刻想過要按下，因為文字獄隨時到來。」另外舞台劇演員韋羅莎亦在Ig的限時動態，以英文留言轟警方。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/85fIXt_ZNBK5O_rPntqNq07Z1u4=/720x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WGQ23HWMLZDETJYYJEU5R6TTPY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F85fIXt_ZNBK5O_rPntqNq07Z1u4%3D%2F720x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWGQ23HWMLZDETJYYJEU5R6TTPY.jpg&h=43904015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■柳俊江在網上鬧爆警方制服女孩的行動。資料圖片"}]}